caption: Collection of Debt
created: 20260405120000000
modified: 20260405120000000
title: Policy5540(s2)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The District's efforts to recover from households money owed due to the charging of meals must not have a negative impact on the children involved and shall focus primarily on the adults in the household responsible for providing funds for meal purchases. The District shall consider whether the benefits of potential collections outweigh the costs which would be incurred to achieve those collections.
